### Register a new user (POST)
POST http://localhost:8080/psacms/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "citizen_001@example.com",
  "password": "secure_password",
  "role": "CITIZEN"
}

### Register a new officer (POST)
POST http://localhost:8080/psacms/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "officer_001@example.com",
  "password": "secure_password",
  "role": "OFFICER"
}